Name: Ancient Astra (Blast)
Desc:
[Enchant Force]
Materializes an arrow of the legends to bombard enemies with a powerful attack.
You can control the angle of fire by using the [Up] / [Down] arrow keys. The arrow explodes when it hits the enemy or at the end of its maximum range.

H.Old:
Relic Gauge Cost: 65. Hold the Skill key to periodically shoot arrows at the chosen angle. When the arrow explodes, it attacks up to 12 enemies at 1440% damage 10 times. The first arrow's angle of fire cannot be adjusted and flies straight forward.
Reduces incoming damage from enemy attacks including those that deals damage based on Max HP by 60%.
Cooldown: 60 sec.
H.New:
Relic Gauge Cost: 65 per 1 sec. Hold the key to periodically fire arrows at a set angle.
The arrow explosion attacks up to 12 enemies at 1440% Damage 10 times.
Damage TAKEN -60% including Max HP-based Damage
Cooldown: 60 sec.
